    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is in pristine, flawless condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away and sparkling clean. It looks and drives like a total dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
