    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered since day one. It honestly looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
