    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. Featuring a 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission, this unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is impeccably sorted, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock for surgical cornering precision. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring mechanical integrity. The Alpine White finish retains its factory depth with no swirling, while the Novillo leather interior remains taut with zero bolster wear. A turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
